  "response": "Rep. Ryan running for two positions simultaneously would be highly unusual in American politics. Generally, candidates focus on one major race at a time to avoid conflicts of interest and logistical issues. Additionally, campaigning for both a House seat and the position of Vice President would present significant challenges in terms of time, resources, and voter perception.\n\nIf you have specific details about which Rep. Ryan (first name, state, etc.) you are referring to, please provide more information so that I can give you a more accurate answer based on the latest available data up to October 2023.",
